About Dataset
This dataset captures essential information for analyzing and managing warehouse inventory and logistics operations. It reflects real-world warehouse conditions across 3,204 records from the year 2024, including data on inventory levels, demand patterns, item storage locations, handling costs, and operational performance.

It is intended to support tasks such as layout planning, inventory control, demand forecasting, and warehouse performance evaluation. By providing comprehensive metrics and performance indicators, this dataset enables data-driven decision-making for efficient warehouse management.

ðŸŽ¯ Purpose
This dataset is suitable for:

Analyzing warehouse space and inventory usage

Forecasting demand and restocking needs

Monitoring stock availability and turnover

Evaluating warehouse performance using key indicators

Supporting logistics planning and inventory simulations

ðŸ”‘ Target Variable
KPI_score (float, 0â€“1+): A composite performance score calculated from factors such as fulfillment rate, stockout frequency, layout efficiency, inventory turnover, and holding cost. This variable reflects the overall operational efficiency of each inventory item.

ðŸŒŸ Key Features
Feature Description
item_id Unique identifier for each inventory item
category Item type or product category
stock_level Current quantity of the item in stock
reorder_point Threshold at which the item should be reordered
reorder_frequency_days Typical interval (in days) between restocking
lead_time_days Delivery time required after placing a reorder
daily_demand Average daily demand for the item
demand_std_dev Demand variability across recent periods
item_popularity_score Normalized score representing historical demand
storage_location_id Identifier for the itemâ€™s storage location
zone Warehouse zone where the item is stored
picking_time_seconds Time needed to retrieve the item from its location
handling_cost_per_unit Cost associated with handling one unit of the item
unit_price Selling price per unit of the item
holding_cost_per_unit_day Daily storage cost per unit
stockout_count_last_month Count of stockouts in the last 30 days
order_fulfillment_rate Percentage of orders successfully fulfilled
total_orders_last_month Total orders received for this item in a month
turnover_ratio Sales-to-inventory ratio indicating stock movement
layout_efficiency_score Efficiency of the storage layout for the item
last_restock_date Date of the most recent inventory replenishment (in 2024)
forecasted_demand_next_7d Estimated demand for the next 7 days
KPI_score Performance score used as the target variable